dalam badan kau.

00:30:32.551 --> 00:30:33.926
Semoga bahagia!

00:30:34.135 --> 00:30:37.593
<i>Aku dah kahwin
Tharagamangalam aku.</i>

00:30:48.843 --> 00:30:50.468
Buah hatiku...

00:30:51.426 --> 00:30:54.510
